questions.question: Did you receive both packages of cigarettes we asked you to try?
Did you try both types of cigarettes we sent you?
Why didn't you try both types of cigarettes?
Did you smoke the first 4 packs of cigarettes you received before smoking the other four packs?
Let me just make sure I have it right. The cigarettes you smoked first were not the ones you received first. That is, you actually smoked the other cigarettes first. Is that correct?

options.no: Repeat Q1E. If answer to question IE is still no, Terminate and Return
